### ==========================================
### 数据分析模块 API 测试
### ==========================================

### 0. 获取 Token
# @name login
POST http://localhost:18081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "XiyuAdmin2026!"
}

@token = {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 1. 正常流程：获取 Dashboard 数据
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. 正常流程：中标率趋势
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard?type=winRate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. 正常流程：投标数据统计
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard?type=biddingStats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. 正常流程：竞争对手分析
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard?type=competitors
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 正常流程：区域分布
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard?type=region
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 正常流程：产品线分析
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard?type=productLines
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 边界：不支持的分析类型
GET http://localhost:18081/api/analytics/dashboard?type=unsupported_type
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
